==English==
===Pronunciation===
*(''verb''): rēsprā', /riːˈspreɪ/, /<tt>ri:'spreI</tt>/
*(''noun''): rē'sprā, /ˈriːspreɪ/, /<tt>'ri:spreI</tt>/
[[Category:English heteronyms]]
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-eɪ|-eɪ]]

===Transitive verb===
{{en-verb}}

#To spray (a vehicle) with paint, either to change its colour to repair damage to the [[paintwork]].
#:''My car's got a big scratch down one side &mdash; I'll have to get it resprayed.''

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

#An act of respraying.
#:''I bought a second-hand car but I don't like the colour, so I'm taking it in for a respray.''